ount": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672319}, {"id": 113948, "content": "有些人虽然看起来弱小无比，但是他的潜力无限。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741053}, {"id": 113949, "content": "天降正义", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 261234}, {"id": 114717, "content": "游泳健身請問需要瞭解一下嗎？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 61731}, {"id": 113950, "content": "炸弹人：对敌人要赶尽杀绝，但一定记得给自己留后路！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 676353}, {"id": 113951, "content": "最后一炮：没有什么是一发贫铀解决不了的，如果有，那就多来几发", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741523}, {"id": 113952, "content": "别在我的坟前哭、挡了我捡负担的路", "image": "img/option/option/20160907144646hPjowWKY1EZer4Sa", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 501377}, {"id": 114208, "content": "疼讯：想一想，不充钱你会变得更强吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 505940}, {"id": 113953, "content": "英雄不朽", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699889}, {"id": 113954, "content": "别在我的坟前哭、挡了我捡负担的路", "image": "img/option/option/20160907144703XYo8qW3aHTuFODws", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 501377}, {"id": 113955, "content": "刺客信条:我们隐藏与黑暗之中却耕耘这光明。", "image": "img/option/option/20160907145417o6PERL1I483w5kQp", "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747481}, {"id": 113956, "content": "贪吃蛇大作战：小蛇的时候看见大蛇就去怼 赢了直接变大蛇 输了大不了重来 不会损失什么 而等你变成大蛇的时候 就会默默的吃豆 不会去杀人 因为死了损失太大 还要时刻注意刚出生的小蛇\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157537}, {"id": 113957, "content": "i wanna系列： 失败不可怕，重要的是从失败中吸取教训", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 120781}, {"id": 113958, "content": "没什么好说的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749374}, {"id": 121638, "content": "使命召唤：永远不要指望队友会冲锋，一切只能靠自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 783564}, {"id": 113959, "content": "说源氏很6的一般都只会玩76", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149075}, {"id": 114215, "content": "芦苇微微和一笑奈何，大神求关爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 751061}, {"id": 113960, "content": "英雄联盟：生活各种不爽的时候只想坑别人。WAIT！所以说有没有可能昨天喷我的人也是这样？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166840}, {"id": 113961, "content": "奇迹暖暖：颜值高穿什么衣服都好看。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713786}, {"id": 113962, "content": "血源：整个游戏设定都是非常规阴暗色彩。不同选择不同结局也增加了游戏丰富性。整个游戏难度可以说挺大的。对新手玩家不太友好。上手须谨慎。但画风 故事 操作 都是这个游戏的一大亮点 尤其是世界观。 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749443}, {"id": 113963, "content": "万事皆允，万物皆虚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 573819}, {"id": 113964, "content": "尽管怂，不要莽。", "image": "img/option/option/20160907153446WvxURsyw8uiPbpQg.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 199957}, {"id": 114220, "content": "奇迹暖暖：颜值高身材好的披一破麻袋都好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133243}, {"id": 113965, "content": "冒险岛，只有前进才知道前方到底是什么样子的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749451}]}